            <Title>The significant fact about Melchizedek is that he</Title>
            <Text>The significant fact about Melchizedek is that he was a priest of God, the Most High God (El Elyon). Melchizedek was representing God and bringing the honor of God to Abram. Melchizedek’s purpose was not to heap worldly praise and honor upon Abram, but to heap godly praise and honor.&quot;
